	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />It looks really good but the dark ground stands out too much and I don't understand what the dark ground is supposed to be.<br /><br />The shading on the top of the upper-right structure and the gate looks weird. Flat planes should have flat shading (unless lit by a nearby point light). I noticed you applied the same weird shading to this other pic:<br /><br /><img src="https://i.imgur.com/GJ5IiD5.png" alt="Image" />

		

		</td>
	</tr>
