		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I'm not sure the palette used mainly for the paths is netting you enough to be worth keeping if you want an extra palette. This is a fairly quick edit:<br /><img src="https://i.imgur.com/mH0eSS4.png" alt="Image" /><br /><br />Will this path style look worse than what you had even if it weren't a quick edit? Sure. But you get another palette, and I think that's a good trade.

		

		</td>
